data.title: Final Presentation
data.msg: Classify notifications by three levels: high, medium, and low.

data.title: Notification System
data.msg: There are a few broadsteps to follow when designing a notification system.

data.title: Design Principle
data.msg: When embarking on notification design, the essential design principle to keep in mind is that they must assist (not impede) people to perform tasks.
